      "layout": "The page primarily uses a full-bleed layout for both light and dark sections, with content centered horizontally but often stretching to near-full width. The hero consists of simple text. Section rhythm is driven by alternating Canvas White and Ink Black backgrounds, creating strong visual breaks. Content is arranged in prominent vertical stacks of large text links, often with smaller descriptive text above. There is no grid usage for content and no visible card structures. Navigation is a minimal, top-bar text-based menu that appears to be sticky or fixed.",
